      • merge

        public IWorkitem merge​(IWorkitem item,
                       IWorkitem otherItem)
        Merge two workitems to a single workitem. Workitem with newer modified date overwrites other workitem. Method is lazy programmed. Method not merge all value and ist not finally tested. Be carefull.
        Parameters:
        item - the first item
        otherItem - the second item
        Returns:
        the merged workitem
